original_content:
Job Description-

This role will blend business acumen with technical proficiency, requiring the ability to understand complex business processes and translate them into effective system configurations. You will be a key player in ensuring our systems accurately reflect business needs and operate efficiently. This position will focus heavily on the developing new processes with technical solutions with the vehicle configuration space. The position will utilize ML and AI to quickly develop solutions.

 • Collaborate with stakeholders across various departments to understand business needs, gather detailed requirements, and document them clearly and concisely using various techniques (e.g., user stories, use cases, process flows). 

• Translate business requirements into technical configurations within our [mention specific system] backend. This includes, but is not limited to:

 • Developing and maintaining configuration specifications.

 • Creating and modifying data mappings and integrations.

 • Implementing and testing new configurations.

 • Troubleshooting and resolving configuration-related issues. 

• Analyze existing data to identify trends, inefficiencies, and areas for improvement. This may involve querying databases, generating reports, and visualizing data using appropriate tools. 

• Identify opportunities to streamline business processes and improve system efficiency through configuration changes and best practices. 

• Thoroughly test configurations to ensure they meet requirements and function as expected. Participate in user acceptance testing (UAT). 

• Maintain comprehensive documentation of system configurations, processes, and troubleshooting steps. 

• Work closely with developers, IT support, and other stakeholders to ensure smooth implementation and ongoing support of system configurations.

Skills Required:

-Strong analytical and problem-solving skills. -Excellent communication, interpersonal, and collaboration skills. -Ability to translate complex technical information into easily understandable terms for non-technical audiences.

Skills Preferred:

-Java experience -SQL experience

Experience Required:

-ML experience and implementation experience

Experience Preferred:

-Experience with Agile methodologies is a plus. -Experience with vehicle configuration is a plus.

This role is a crucial bridge between business acumen and technical expertise, responsible for aligning complex business processes with effective system configurations. As a key player in our organization, you will ensure our systems accurately reflect evolving business needs and operate at peak efficiency. Your primary focus will be on developing new processes and leveraging cutting-edge technologies like machine learning (ML) and artificial intelligence (AI) to deliver innovative solutions within the vehicle configuration space.

Key Responsibilities:
- Collaborate extensively with stakeholders across various departments to understand business requirements, gather detailed specifications, and document them using industry-standard techniques (e.g., user stories, use cases, process flows)
- Translate business requirements into technical configurations within our [mention specific system] backend, including developing and maintaining configuration specifications, creating and modifying data mappings and integrations, implementing and testing new configurations, and troubleshooting configuration-related issues
- Analyze existing data to identify trends, inefficiencies, and areas for improvement, leveraging tools for querying databases, generating reports, and visualizing data
- Proactively identify opportunities to streamline business processes and enhance system efficiency through configuration changes and the application of industry best practices
- Thoroughly test configurations to ensure they meet requirements and function as expected, actively participating in user acceptance testing (UAT)
- Maintain comprehensive documentation of system configurations, processes, and troubleshooting steps
- Work closely with developers, IT support, and other stakeholders to facilitate smooth implementation and ongoing support of system configurations

Required Skills:
- Strong analytical and problem-solving skills, with the ability to identify and address complex technical and business challenges
- Excellent communication, interpersonal, and collaboration skills, enabling you to translate complex technical information into easily understandable terms for non-technical audiences
- Demonstrated proficiency in managing multiple priorities and delivering high-quality work within tight deadlines

Preferred Skills:
- Hands-on experience with Java programming language
- Proficiency in SQL for database querying and data analysis

Required Experience:
- Proven track record of successfully implementing machine learning (ML) and artificial intelligence (AI) solutions in a professional setting
- Demonstrated experience in translating business requirements into technical configurations and system enhancements

Preferred Experience:
- Experience working within Agile methodologies, contributing to the iterative development and continuous improvement of solutions
- Familiarity with vehicle configuration processes and industry-specific best practices

Tools & Technologies:
- [Mention specific system] backend configuration tools
- Data querying and reporting tools (e.g., SQL, Tableau, Power BI)
- Machine learning and artificial intelligence platforms (e.g., TensorFlow, Keras, PyTorch)

Work Environment & Expectations:
- Collaborative, cross-functional team environment with a focus on delivering high-quality, innovative solutions
- Ability to work independently and as part of a team, demonstrating strong ownership and accountability for assigned tasks
- Willingness to adapt to changing priorities and requirements, while maintaining a solutions-oriented mindset
